[2C[3A]0;⠐ Story writing assistance]0;⠂ Story writing assistance[2D[3B[2C[7A[1mThe Lighthouse Keeper's Last Night[2C[1B[22m                                  [2C[1BOld[1CTomas[1Chad[1Ctended[1Cthe[1Clighthouse[1Con[1CSkerry[1CPoint[1Cfor[1Cforty-one[1Cyears.[1CHe[1Cknew[1Cevery[1Cgroan[1Cof[1Cthe[1Ciron[1Cstair,[1Cevery[1Cmood[1Cof[1Cthe[1Clamp,[1Cevery[1Cshape[1Cthe[1Cfog[1Ctook[1Cas[1Cit[1Crolled[1Cin[1Cfrom[1Cthe[1Cnorth.[1B                                                                                                                                                                                                                    [1B[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[1B[38;5;246m❯ [39m[7m [27m                                                                                                                                                                                                                 [1B[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
[2C[38;5;246mesc[1Cto[1Cinterrupt[175C◉[1Cxhigh[1C·[1C/effort[39m
[2C[3A]0;⠐ Story writing assistance]0;⠂ Story writing assistance[2D[3B[4A  On his last night before retirement, a small boat appeared in the bay — too small for those waters, too late in the season. Tomas climbed to the lamp room and turned the beam toward it. The boat held a single  [1B  passenger:[1Ca[1Cboy[1Cof[1Cmaybe[1Cten,[1Crowing[1Cbadly,[1Csoaked[1Cto[1Cthe[1Cbone.[1B                                                                                                                                                                                                                    [1B[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
[38;5;246m❯ [39m[7m [27m
[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
[2C[38;5;246mesc[1Cto[1Cinterrupt[39m
[2C[3A]0;⠐ Story writing assistance[2D[3B[4A  Tomas met him at the rocks with a blanket and a thermos. "Where did you come from?"                                                                                                                               [1B   [2B[38;5;246m❯ [39m[7m [27m               
[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
[2C[38;5;246mesc[1Cto[1Cinterrupt[39m
[2C[3A[2D[3B[4A  The boy looked up at the lighthouse, then back at Tomas, and smiled like he'd found something he'd been searching for.                                                                                            [1B   [2B[38;5;246m❯ [39m[7m [27m               
[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
[2C[38;5;246mesc[1Cto[1Cinterrupt[39m
[2C[3A]0;⠂ Story writing assistance[2D[3B[4A  "My grandfather built this place," he said. "He told me to come see it before they shut the light off. He said the keeper would know him."                                                                        [1B   [2B[38;5;246m❯ [39m[7m [27m               
[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
[2C[38;5;246mesc[1Cto[1Cinterrupt[39m
[2C[3A]0;⠐ Story writing assistance]0;⠂ Story writing assistance[2D[3B[4A  Tomas hadn't told anyone he was leaving. Hadn't told anyone the light was being decommissioned at dawn. He looked at the boy's face — the same stubborn jaw, the same grey eyes as the man who'd trained him      [1B  forty-one[1Cyears[1Cago,[1Cthe[1Cman[1Cwho'd[1Cbeen[1Cburied[1Cfor[1Cthirty.[1B                                                                                                                                                                                                                    [1B[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
[38;5;246m❯ [39m[7m [27m
[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
[2C[38;5;246mesc[1Cto[1Cinterrupt[39m
[2C[3A[2D[3B[4A  "Yes," Tomas said quietly. "The keeper knows him."                                                                                                                                                                [1B   [2B[38;5;246m❯ [39m[7m [27m               
[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
[2C[38;5;246mesc[1Cto[1Cinterrupt[39m
[2C[3A]0;⠐ Story writing assistance[2D[3B[4A  They sat together until sunrise, and when the light finally went dark, neither of them was alone.                                                                                                                 [1B   [2B[38;5;246m❯ [39m[7m [27m               
[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[39m
